{"tid":979633,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"請問會唔會有專一既射手座","createTime":"2019-01-12T21:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T06:25:53.000Z","uid":219876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e195654f4ad9f52c5b0e7ffbc089c761686347b9","tid":979633,"uid":219876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T21:34:57.000Z","msg":"宜家同另一半已經一齊2個月<br />\n見面時間唔算多 平均1個星期1日<br />\n因為我地都要返學 所以無咩時間出黎<br />\n到目前為止我地都好中意對方<br />\n.<br />\n但係今年7月佢就會去台灣返工<br />\n我會留係香港 所以就會變long d <br />\n可能見面既時間會比以前更少<br />\n我唔知可以點去留住佢<br />\n.<br />\n好驚佢去到果邊識左第二個<br />\n因為我之前問過佢: 你會唔會唔要我<br />\n佢淨係答話: 今年之內都唔會<br />\n就係因為呢句令我好唔開心<br />\n.<br />\n我知道射手座都係貪玩既<br />\n所以想問大家有咩方法<br />\n可以去keep住呢段關係"},{"pid":"9a6069c71760fc416d2b238049264438b733552b","tid":979633,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T21:36:16.000Z","msg":"食屎啦你"},{"pid":"43298d363c01fee2776644293f49f2a9a14d84c8","tid":979633,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T21:36:20.000Z","msg":".<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97aecf7beb157df2615fe2cc329a0ac18be67fd","tid":979633,"uid":84478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T21:41:14.000Z","msg":"唔理咩星座都好 同未玩夠嘅人勉強維繫關係好難 何況仲要long d<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe129e1232c9956e24396d2de79cd7990e0cbbfe","tid":979633,"uid":219876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e97aecf7beb157df2615fe2cc329a0ac18be67fd","tid":979633,"uid":84478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T21:41:14.000Z","msg":"唔理咩星座都好 同未玩夠嘅人勉強維繫關係好難 何況仲要long d<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T21:50:23.000Z","msg":"我見佢宜家都對我好好<br />\n有時仲會煮飯比我食<br />\n陪我去行街<br />\n佢成日都好似知道我諗咩<br />\n真係唔可以無左佢